result.name: Peking Garden

reviews.text: Food was good, service was terrible. We were seated in the bar, waited 15 minutes and finally caught someone to take our order, never saw our waiter after that. Had to keep grabbing staff members as they walked by to get what we needed. Waited 45 minutes to get our food. Experience ruin our last night in Hong Kong.
Soup no taste ... 糟溜魚片 sauce too thick and too sweet... Services was rush ... Not relaxing dinner

This is one of the best place that you can have Peking Duck in Hong Kong. I have visited the Taikoo Peking Garden two days ago. The staffs are helpful but sometimes as shortage of staffs, they may answer your call a little bit late. Overall the quality of the foods which are good for what you paid.

Peking Garden used to very very good and was toted to be a premium restaurant, at least along the Maxim's Group chain, but it didn't strike me as anything special. Returning on a Sunday evening at 6pm, service was already bustling and busy. The menu, while long, didn't seem to have a wide variety of options. Two Peking ducks were ordered in advance. A little disappointed in their selection of noodles and non-pork friendly dishes. There was only one fried noodle dish and the rest were all soup noodles. Thankfully the removed the pork and substituted with mushrooms. Overall, the food tasted OK, would probably be able to find better Peking duck elsewhere.

Service not too polite. Peking duck is nothing compared with real one in Beijing. Even a local restaurant in Beijing has better one.

The skin has too much meat and not crispy. The bread wrap for Peking duck is too thick and smell bad

Forgot to say that the Peking duck can be cooked in one way or 3 ways. The other 2 ways are optional. We only ordered one way. Make sure you can bring the remain of the duck to take out. The servers will not ask u. The remain of the duck is big. In fact, the 1 way cooking consumed less than 1/2 of the duck.

result.name: 北京樓

reviews.text: 太古城北京樓我們中伏了😭😭

應該是0星，絕對不會再去，星期六晚跟家人吃飯，本来想定6:30但接待的說只可以定6:00或8:00並一定要2小時內離開，已經覺得是無理的限制，入座後枱與枱之間差不多一點空間也沒有，由於侍應要趕快上枱迫人食快D，個個侍應趕來趕去有什麼就互相大聲喊叫，態度超級超級冇禮貌，由於我們的枱正正在收碗盤附近，晦氣的待應整晚得登大力扔擲客人用完的碗碟入收碗盤入面，每隔10-15 分鐘如是，進食環境十分惡劣，其中一次最大的阿頭在某待應極大力掟碟後叫了他入後面應該是教訓他，但我們客人不會理你如何教你的伙記，你的伙記將客人當出氣袋，悪劣態度並不是一時三刻形成或可以改變，這些人根本要炒，食物也是馬馬虎虎，一是很淡一是很咸，北京烤鴨只有肉，皮是軟的，一口肥膩，總之整晚家人的用饍心情嚴重受影響，根本是貼錢買難受。

不知所謂
片皮鴨片肉多個片皮
服務態度奇差 
啲侍應為咗方便下下都隔咗幾張枱大聲溝通
收拾時碗碟大大力掟落盤 
佢哋睇唔清楚我哋畫乜食物
下下好似質問人，話：我睇唔清楚你畫乜，你畫好少少先啦
污糟嘅枱布碗碟周圍擺，仲要放正喺客人飯枱隔離
同一張枱左手擺緊啲收咗嘅污糟碗碟
右手係度片緊隻鴨。
同一集團的美中鴨子，
明明檔次較北京樓低
服務唔叫好得去邊
但食物方面比北京樓好好多
no more next time

叫了甜品，要求最後才上甜品，可是飯都未食完，點品就上哂，問可否食完飯最後才上，但佢話廚房要收!!!!所以要現在上，如果我吾要可以cancel, 當時只係晚上九點幾(但當天是十一點關門）

這是什麼服務態度⋯⋯好失望，其實應該是零星

裝修環境都算有品味，可色生意好，擺枱密咗D。
今晚睇過餐牌，有幾欵菜式可能幾受歡迎，都用貼紙加了價。
我太太唔係好食得棘，所以我點冇棘椒圖案餸菜，
豉汁炒帶子，點知都中伏，整碟餸都是棘油包住，真攞命！
